uiEntry.title: root
uiEntry.script:
local this = UIComponent(Address)
function ShowMenu(name) for i = 0, this:ChildCount() - 1 do local child = UIComponent(this:Find(i)) child:SetVisible(child:Id() == name) end end

uiEntry.title: dropdown_weather
uiEntry.tooltip: Certain weather conditions will affect the way you fight a battle.||Heavy rain can dampen firearms - resulting in slower firing rates and even misfires.||A soggy battlefield will prevent cannonballs from bouncing, meaning they will not travel as far and do less damage.||Movement can be affected as well - for example, heavy snowfalls will slow down an army as it struggles through it.
